&lt;p&gt;At Horace Mann, we&#39;re committed to helping educators and their families recover when the unexpected happens. We are seeking an experienced &lt;strong&gt;Bodily Injury Adjuster II&lt;/strong&gt; to investigate, evaluate, negotiate, and resolve auto bodily injury claims while delivering an exceptional customer experience.&lt;/p&gt;
